Package: cleanRfish
Type: Package
Title: Trajectory Cleaning and Smoothing for Movement Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Jack", "L. Manera", email = "Jack.Manera@monash.edu", role = c("aut","cre"),
         comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0003-7947-6473")))
Description: Tools to identify discontinuities in two-dimensional animal
    trajectories and to smooth positions while preserving temporal alignment.
    Includes robust velocity-based outlier detection and Savitzky-Golay
    smoothing, plus helpers for visual overlays on videos.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/JLManera/cleanRfish, https://jlmanera.github.io/cleanRfish
BugReports: https://github.com/JLManera/cleanRfish/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    stats,
    signal,
    zoo,
    data.table,
    purrr,
    mgcv,
    mixtools
Suggests:
    FKF,
    KFAS,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    ggplot2,
    tidyr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
